OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779789943
OL,3,C13-year-old dies after reports of
OL,4,Cdifficulty in Halifax reservoir
OL,6,FA teenager has been pronounced dead
OL,7,Fafter being pulled from water near
OL,8,FHalifax.
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire police say the body of
OL,11,Fa 13-year-old boy has been pulled from
OL,12,Fthe water at Leadbeater Dam on Lumb
OL,13,FLamb near Halifax at around 3.20pm on
OL,14,FMonday 25th May.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital where he was
OL,17,Flater pronounced dead.
