OL,3,C13-year-old dies after reports of
OL,4,Cdifficulty in Halifax reservoir
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the force said
OL,7,Fofficers were called to reports a
OL,8,Fteenager had gotten into difficulty in
OL,9,Fthe water.
OL,11,FThey added: "Enquiries are ongoing by
OL,12,FCalderdale CID, however there are not
OL,13,Fbelieved to be any suspicious
OL,14,Fcircumstances."
